
# SCRATCH PROJECT -  Earth's Defense

## PLANNING

### Sprites

1. Ship
2. Asteroid
3. Earth
4. Laser

### Functions

#### Ship

1. Movement (Face Y+ and move +-x only)
2. Counter for laser + asteroid collision

#### Laser

1. Movement (move +y only, no x)
2. Impact (delete when collision with asteroid or reach max Y)

### Asteroid

1. fall (-y)
2. clone (to start) then explode on collision with laser or edge
